I’m considering if there might be an actual bug in the defaultPreset. It seems that the moduleId of defaultPreset is set to config.id, so having the signature moduleId explicitly derived from config.id guarantees that we’re aligned with both default and extra canonical settings. I think I need to update the helper function to address this issue properly. I want to ensure everything is functioning smoothly!"}]}

